    "Virtual Assistances and Conversational Commerce 4.3.1.",
    "Started Discussed CommerceConversational buying that is, direct consumer purchases made using chat interfaces is a clear trend.",
    "These systems handle payment processes, answer questions, improve upselling & help product discovery by using LLMs trained with specific prompts. Imagine this series on WhatsApp:  Customer: \"Desperate for a vegan leather tote bag under $200.\"",
    " Bot: \"Surely!\"",
    "Would you go for a sloppy or more disciplined approach?"
  ]
